title: Enchanted April (1992)
description:
Compressed video with fitted English subtitles.

A new improved version of this movie expected to
become available today 3/8/09. 

It will not be full of commercials and not have to
be edited like my previous one was.

I shall try to seamlessly fit my subtitles to the
compressed version and upload the result in the
next few days.

I will label it version 2 and keep both the original
and the "updated" version for some time.
